const articleHtml = `<p>Local payments via HedgeFlows are the way to transfer funds internationally leveraging our partner network with access to the local payment scheme. This can be a cost-effective and fast alternative to traditional SWIFT payments. All pricing plants HedgeFlows include a set number of complimentary Local payments.</p> 
 <h3>Local Payments in Euros = SEPA payments</h3> <p>Sending Euros via the Single Euro Payment Area (SEPA) is one of the most popular Local payments routes. The following countries are included in SEPA:</p> 
